Positive test
valid input --> system --> expected result

- happy path
- checks if system works as expected
- checks if features are working as intended


------------------------------------------------------------------

Negative test
invalid imput --> system --> error

- verifying if the system correctly rejects invalid data
- what happens when the input is not correct
e.g. invalid passoword, too long text exceeding the limit, temperature out of range, forbidden characters, invalid data or unexpected user behaviour
